org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.objectinspector

Interface StructField

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseStructObjectInspector.MyField, ReflectionStructObjectInspector.MyField, StandardStructObjectInspector.MyField, UnionStructObjectInspector.MyField

    @InterfaceAudience.Public
 @InterfaceStability.Stable
public interface StructField
    Classes implementing this interface are considered to represent a field of a struct for this serde package.
